name: my_friends_among_the_sprites_ii
description:
A collaboration between the_side_hustle & sgt_slaughtermelon.
"1 pixel lines and dots and all the rainbows and life that grow out of them. I still remember all the little screens and dot matrices I grew up with, and they’ve taken on a life of their own in my imagination. I don’t spend all my time with them, but I have friends - friends among the sprites."
